thread.title: Time Warner posts 14 pct rise in quarterly profit
thread.title_full: Time Warner posts 14 pct rise in quarterly profit | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Time Warner posts 14 pct rise in quarterly profit
text:
Aug 5 Time Warner Inc reported a 14 percent rise in quarterly profit, helped by higher revenue at its Turner network and Warner Bros. studio.
The company's net income rose to $971 million, or $1.16 per share, in the second quarter ended June 30, from $850 million, or 95 cents per share, a year earlier.
Revenue rose 8 percent to $7.35 billion. (Reporting by Sagarika Jaisinghani and Anya George Tharakan in Bengaluru; Editing by Maju Samuel)
